### Key Pain Points Identified
- **Information Asymmetry:** Traditional VC due diligence costs вӮ№5вҖ“50 lakh per startup and is unavailable to retail investors.
- **Speed:** Institutional evaluation takes 3вҖ“6 months; AI-driven due diligence reduces this to hours.
- **Compliance Gap:** No Indian crowd-investing platform currently uses on-chain KYC/AML with regulatory-grade security tokens.
- **Transparency Deficit:** Fund allocation decisions in crowd platforms are opaque вҖ” no explainable AI layer.

