### 4D: Summary Gap Analysis

**What IntelliStake Adds Over All Prior Work:**
1. **End-to-End Integration:** No paper in literature links AI valuation вҶ’ portfolio optimization вҶ’ blockchain execution in one platform.
2. **Indian Startup Context:** All prior ML papers use US/European/Chinese equity data. IntelliStake is purpose-built for Indian startup corpus.
3. **Trust Score as Governing Signal:** The R.A.I.S.E. composite trust score (GitHub velocity + Founder Pedigree + Market Traction) replaces traditional credit ratings and drives all downstream decisions.
4. **Live Explainability at Scale:** 37,699 SHAP narratives on the actual model вҖ” not just model cards.
5. **Regulatory Compliance by Design:** ERC-3643, KYC/AML on-chain, aligned with EU AI Act XAI requirements.

