## SLIDE 7 вҖ” METHODOLOGY & IMPLEMENTATION

**Slide Title:** Methodology вҖ” From Raw Data to Investment Decision

### Data Pipeline (5 Phases)
1. **Ingest:** Scraped 74,577 Indian startup records from 6 sources using async Dask pipeline
2. **Clean:** Entity resolution (fuzzywuzzy threshold 88) вҶ’ 403 MB lake, 64 features per startup
3. **Enrich:** VADER/FinBERT sentiment on 5,000 news articles; GitHub velocity for 4,081 repos; 199 MCA financial audits
4. **Model:** Trained Stacked Ensemble (XGB+LGB+CatBoost+MLP) with 5-fold CV + log1p transform
5. **Govern:** R.A.I.S.E. trust score вҶ’ BL portfolio вҶ’ Oracle push вҶ’ Escrow release

### Trust Score Formula
```
Trust Score = 0.55 Г— GitHub_Velocity
            + 0.25 Г— Founder_Pedigree
            + 0.20 Г— Market_Traction
            
Where Market_Traction = 0.6 Г— Sentiment + 0.4 Г— Web_Traffic
```

### BL Portfolio Formula
```
Ој_BL = [(П„ОЈ)вҒ»В№ + PбөҖО©вҒ»В№P]вҒ»В№ В· [(П„ОЈ)вҒ»В№ПҖ + PбөҖО©вҒ»В№Q]

Where:
  ПҖ = equilibrium returns (market-cap priors)
  Q = AI-generated views (trust score вҶ’ return uplift)
  О© = uncertainty matrix (R.A.I.S.E. confidence)
```

### Monte Carlo Formula
```
daily_return ~ N(Ој_BL / 252,  Пғ_trust / вҲҡ252)
Simulated over 10,000 paths Г— 252 trading days
```

### Implementation Highlights
- 16 parallel workers for risk audit (ThreadPoolExecutor)
- 6 parallel RSS workers with exponential backoff (2/4/8s)
- VADER Singleton instantiation (0.001ms/call overhead)
- Model persistence вҖ” no retraining on re-run

