## SLIDE 11 вҖ” ARM 4: OVERALL PLATFORM WORKING

**Slide Title:** Overall Working вҖ” The Investor Journey End-to-End

### The 5-Step Investor Journey
```
STEP 1 вҖ” DISCOVER рҹ”Қ
  Investor logs in вҶ’ KYC wallet verified (ERC-3643) 
  вҶ’ Browse 74,577 startups on Galaxy Heatmap (X=Funding, Y=Trust, Opacity=Survival)
  вҶ’ Explore Company Profile deep-dive

STEP 2 вҖ” ANALYSE рҹ“Ҡ
  Select startup вҶ’ AI Valuation Engine predicts вӮ№ value (RВІ=0.9738)
  вҶ’ SHAP Explainer shows why (feature contributions)
  вҶ’ Risk Auditor shows Trust Score breakdown
  вҶ’ Sentiment Terminal shows FinBERT headlines
  вҶ’ Hype Detector flags if anomalous

STEP 3 вҖ” SIMULATE рҹҺІ
  View Black-Litterman portfolio allocation
  вҶ’ Monte Carlo 10K paths (VaR, CVaR)
  вҶ’ Digital Twin sliders: what-if scenario analysis
  вҶ’ Backtest: how would this have performed since 2018?

STEP 4 вҖ” EXECUTE вӣ“пёҸ
  Approve investment вҶ’ Oracle Bridge pushes trust score on-chain
  вҶ’ If trust вүҘ 0.50: MilestoneEscrow releases tranche
  вҶ’ If trust < 0.35: freezeMilestoneFunding() called
  вҶ’ Investment Committee (Quant+Auditor+Newsroom+Manager) votes

STEP 5 вҖ” REPORT рҹ“„
  AI generates investment memo (ReportLab)
  вҶ’ Full audit log in Oracle Event Log
  вҶ’ Portfolio performance tracked live
```

